        <abstract> 
<p>Asks MEL to translate page of paper by Sven Lovén ["Ny art af Cirripedia", <hi rend="italic">Ofvers. K. Vetensk. Acad. Forh. Stockholm</hi> 1 (1844): 192–4]. CD is "dreadfully interested" in the barnacles [<hi rend="italic">Alepas squalicola</hi>] described.</p> 
            <p>Hopes Charles Lyell’s "craters of Denudation" prosper.</p>
